---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
import ContentSection from "~/components/content-section.astro";
---

<ContentSection title="About me" id="about">
  <Fragment slot="lead">
    <p class="text-center text-sm md:px-16 md:text-lg">
      Hello! I'm Adithya Krishna Eemani, an Entrepreneur and Co-Founder at <a
        target="_blank"
        href="https://velopulent.com/"
      >
        <span class="text-primary">Velopulent</span></a
      >. We excel at crafting captivating static websites and developing
      efficient software products.
      <br />
      <br />
      With a strong background in Computer Science and Engineering, specializing
      in <span class="text-primary"
        >Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning</span
      >, I'm committed to making a transformative impact. I work tirelessly to <span
        class="text-primary">create innovative and efficient code</span
      > that empowers businesses and improves people's lives. If you're looking for
      a motivated and <span class="text-primary">skilled developer</span> with a
      passion for innovation, then I would love to hear from you!
    </p>
  </Fragment>
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 lg:flex-row">
    <a
      href="/RESUME.pdf"
      target="_blank"
      class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-lg border-2 border-current px-6 py-4"
    >
      <Icon pack="mdi" name="book" class="h-8" />
      <span>My Resume</span>
    </a>
    <a
      href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/adithyakrishnaeemani"
      target="_blank"
      class="flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-lg border-2 border-current px-6 py-4 lg:w-48"
    >
      <Icon pack="mdi" name="linkedin" class="h-8 md:h-8 mr-2" />
      <span class="text-base">Connect</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</ContentSection>
